{"id": "1454208820091031684", "channel_id": "1454208820091031684", "type": 0, "author_id": "594053406537023518", "author_name": "namielle_4214", "author_bot": false, "content": "大佬們好<:S_threat:1400771719404196010> \n新手剛玩三天，目前主線推到第四章，隊伍如圖。\n想請問往事失落以前的卡池推薦抽哪個? 聽說彌利亞姆快復刻了所以先不考慮抽深海。\n關於 200 銀鑰自選，我聽大家說卡斯托爾很強，但XP上挺喜歡克萊門汀跟熔毀朵爾，有點糾結。\n目前沒多少角色可用，對於接下來該組什麼隊伍完全沒頭緒。有什麼建議的話十分感謝<:Sendflowers:1400771545370067118>", "timestamp": "2025-12-26T20:26:40.603000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-12-26T20:40:38.645000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1454208821160575148", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1772985, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1454208820091031684/1454208821160575148/image.png?ex=69ccd6c0&is=69cb8540&hm=3f51b82f7558d458194f63f631dfac96ce53f2929c61a751dcc3ba6962ae1f93&"}, {"id": "1454208822322401453", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 911251, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1454208820091031684/1454208822322401453/image.png?ex=69ccd6c1&is=69cb8541&hm=14a4288ae29541deb5f0ad9196aacf3987e3e7cebeee5cbdf49400dd96b1b9d9&"}, {"id": "1454208823181967558", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 576890, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1454208820091031684/1454208823181967558/image.png?ex=69ccd6c1&is=69cb8541&hm=a186d934e73f1b1a375c1c59003fae542f745dc082e440129acf662a11c325c2&"}, {"id": "1454208823580557322", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 829242, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1454208820091031684/1454208823580557322/image.png?ex=69ccd6c1&is=69cb8541&hm=82cb7a4ef034b82695437929da47d4c629e151037bcc48cf1b61325bfa001d02&"}, {"id": "1454208824884858961", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 2193474, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1454208820091031684/1454208824884858961/image.png?ex=69ccd6c1&is=69cb8541&hm=d4c2ede66763d1bc3bc05fb0130